Package net.fathomsoft.nova.tree.variables

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Array
    Identifier extension that contains the information describing an array instantiation.
    ArrayAccess
    Value extension that keeps track of any time an array is being accessed.
    FieldDeclaration
    Declaration extension that represents the declaration of a field node type.
    FieldList
    Node extension that contains all of the Fields for a ClassDeclaration.
    InstanceFieldList
    Node extensions that contains all of the public Field instances of a ClassDeclaration.
    StaticFieldList
    Node extensions that contains all of the private Field instances of a ClassDeclaration.
    Variable
    Identifier extension that represents the use of a variable type.
    VariableDeclaration
    Identifier extension that represents something that returns a value.
    VariableDeclarationList
    Node that holds the LocalVariables that a method contains.
